Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:15.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よしっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,マスミ　あんたどこ行ってたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:54.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やだ　なにこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水の音？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.64,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,娘の…様子かい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,確かに　この頃体調を崩しちまってるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:00.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに　原因は分かってるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:04.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,医者にも蟲師にも直せねえ病さ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:08.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ついた男が会いに来なくなったってんでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気が塞いじまって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:14.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,体の具合まで悪くなっちまったんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,毎度のことじゃあるんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.21,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今回のは随分長引いてでね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:27.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,しかし　それは気の病だけとは限りませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,と言いますと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ひとつ　水盤を用意しちゃもらえませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これに姿を映してみてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,影を　映し取られたんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:03.46,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,波のない池に棲む　「水鏡」という蟲がいましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.80,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もとは水銀のような姿をしたものですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:11.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,池の水面に動物の姿が映り込むと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その姿をまねて　陸に上がります
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:19.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして本体の後に付いて回る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:24.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すると　本体の方は少しずつ体力が衰えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:30.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本体が衰えるほど　水鏡は実体を持ち始め
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本体は実体を失っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.75,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そしてやがては　水鏡は本体に成り代わる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:43.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水鏡は水の中の鉱物質を必要とし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:47.99,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,実体を持つと　より濃度の高い水を求めて歩き回る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:53.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水鏡はもともとの姿では自ら動くことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だから　自由に動ける体を欲しがるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それは困る　なんとかならんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.53,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本体と入れ替わる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:07.40,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰の目にも水鏡の姿が見える
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:11.19,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこを本体に鏡に映されると
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:14.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,姿は崩れ　本体も元に戻ります
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　簡単なことじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:21.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　マスミ　お前　手鏡持ってただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:22.97,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこやった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　曇っちまってるんじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:31.01,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,研いでやるから　貸して
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:35.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やめてよ　大事な　鏡なの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自分でやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:14.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめん　ちょっと出てくる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:19.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら　どこ行くのよ　マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また随分曇ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたに研いでほしいから　自分じゃ研がないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あのさ　マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.33,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このところ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.74,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここいら一帯すっかり鏡研ぎの口も減っちまってな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,仕事場変えてみようと思うんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんな　じゃ次はいつ会えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:26.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあな　いつ戻るか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,嫌よ　そんなの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:34.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,俺だって嫌だけど　でも食ってかなきゃならねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分かってくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:41.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　じゃ私　あんたの里で待ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたの嫁になる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.12,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,所帯を持つ気はまだねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　その気になるまで待つよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.88,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おめえみてえな跳ねっ返りの嫁はごめんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:58.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,嫁にするなら　もっと大人しい娘がいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういうわけだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,次の約束はできねえからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:11.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今度鏡が曇ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,悪いが　自分が研いでくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.10,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何やってんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:10.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこにいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.87,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた　あたしになりたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,こんなあたしになりたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:40.48,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前さんにも　水鏡の足音が聞こえ始めたか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:46.02,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,手鏡は研いだか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.63,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そいつに成り代わられたくなかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.55,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,早いとこ研いどけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.38,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,別に代わってやったっていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:11:59.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:02.76,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私はもう私でいたってしかたない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:05.54,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほしいならあげたっていい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:12.16,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あのな　投げ遣りにしてと後悔することもできなくなるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:14.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水鏡と入れ替わるってことは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.24,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自我も実体も失うってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.50,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前は自分の意志で
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:24.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この世に影響を及ぼすことが何一つできないものになるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:32.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いても　いなくても　同じものに…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ああ　そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.37,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なら　今の私と同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:53.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの人にとって　私はそれくらい軽いものだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.85,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私が何を言ったって　何をしたって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんの影響も受けやしない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:09.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,実体があってもなくても同じこと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:17.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこは　さびしいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:28.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だがな　そこよりずっとさびしい所がある
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.79,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲と同じ実体をもたないものたちの棲む世だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:40.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そこは　この世には必要とされないものたちの蠢く暗い所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:45.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲どもに心なんぞはありはしないが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.84,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,多くのものが光を求めて這い出そうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.09,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなさびしい所だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:03.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,相手は実体に姿を映されただけで消えるはかないものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:10.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,血の通う実体を持つということは　それだけで強い力を持つってことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:17.28,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だが　一旦入れ替わると　それも逆転する
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:25.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また暖かい場所へ戻りたければ　自分の身は自分で守るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:37.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,脈が弱い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:39.32,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,鏡は研いだか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.62,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,よし　肌身離さず持ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じき　水鏡が姿を現す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:54.61,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その瞬間を鏡に映すんだ　見逃すな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.04,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.81,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お手洗い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.60,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一人で大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:21.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,戻ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:47.94,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:15.52,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんな所に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.00,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,体が…動かない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.29,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.71,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,入れ替わられちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:51.35,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんなふうに人の周りを付いて回るだけのものになるの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:54.82,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いやだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなの　さびしすぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:00.89,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何よ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.36,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,真似してんじゃないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:41.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当にもうなんともないのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.73,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだ　このバカ娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:46.34,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今日一日くらい大人しくしてなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.65,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.90,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんで消えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:56.31,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　俺もずっと考えてんだがな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.66,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか　眼だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:07.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前の眼に水鏡の姿が映ったんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.37,0:20:13.47,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだ　眼を開けてさえいりゃ　鏡なんか必要ねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:18.91,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やはり実体を持って生きてるってのは
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:22.18,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それだけで充分力を持ってんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:25.70,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうかしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.20,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今まで気が付かなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.56,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんた　よく見ると男前だね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:35.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,髪の色とか変だけと　血筋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,奥さんいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.43,0:20:38.95,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,郷里はどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当にもう治ったみたいですな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:43.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さようで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:46.11,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃ　俺はこの辺で
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.96,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう少しゆっくりしてきなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.42,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お礼もしたいしさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:52.25,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,マスミ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.45,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お前　少しは懲りんか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.30,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,これか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.49,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やはり元の場所に戻ってたか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:41.83,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,付いて来い　もっと山深い池に案内してやる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.93,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,実体はくれてやらんがな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.17,TXT JP (ONLY) G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そんなさびしそうにしてるなよ
